data.description:
This low maintenance stucco home is a 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom open concept home with a split bedroom design.  Constructed in 2019, it is beautifully tiled throughout all main living areas and hallways. The owners suite best describe this large primary bedroom with a large walk in closet, big enough for two, a double sink vanity, and a luxurious walk-in shower. The kitchen's granite countertops and freestanding gas range is a chef's delight. Come home to evening sunsets on your covered patio overlooking your spacious backyard.
Call your favorite Realtor and make an appointment to make this one yours.
